{
    "publish_date": "2014-07-29T17:33:08.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT6M47S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "For nearly 25 years, I wandered.", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "4.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was born in 1968\nto a good family,", 
            "dur": "3.98", 
            "start": "15.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "though we didn&#39;t believe in God.", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "19.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, as I grew\nolder, I began", 
            "dur": "1.77", 
            "start": "22.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make fun of people\nwho thought God was real.", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "23.97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t need somebody\nelse&#39;s make-believe God.", 
            "dur": "4.04", 
            "start": "27.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was certain He wasn&#39;t there.", 
            "dur": "1.69", 
            "start": "31.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "From age 14 to 22, I\nlived entirely for myself.", 
            "dur": "4.478", 
            "start": "35.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was popular in high\nschool, and I partied hard.", 
            "dur": "4.634", 
            "start": "40.308"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I even won two state\nbasketball championships.", 
            "dur": "4.168", 
            "start": "44.942"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "By age 18, I had a\nfull-ride scholarship", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "49.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to play college basketball.", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "51.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt like I was on my way.", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "54.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But four years later, it\nall came crashing down.", 
            "dur": "4.58", 
            "start": "58.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;d made some bad choices.", 
            "dur": "2.66", 
            "start": "62.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And gradually I lost\neverything I had earned.", 
            "dur": "4.21", 
            "start": "65.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll never forget the day,\nat age 22 on a Thursday,", 
            "dur": "5.97", 
            "start": "69.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I decided to end my life.", 
            "dur": "1.998", 
            "start": "75.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I sat in the school\ncafeteria that day", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "80.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "thinking about how I\nwas going to do it,", 
            "dur": "2.92", 
            "start": "82.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how I would spend\nmy last weekend", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "85.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on earth, when I overheard two\ngirls at a nearby table talking", 
            "dur": "5.56", 
            "start": "87.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about fasting and prayer.", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "93.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I interrupted, asking\nthem what fasting was.", 
            "dur": "4.31", 
            "start": "96.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of them told\nme it was something", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "100.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they did when they\nwanted help from God.", 
            "dur": "3.86", 
            "start": "102.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It seemed so silly, but\nI listened, intrigued.", 
            "dur": "4.34", 
            "start": "106.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That night, all\nalone, I knelt down", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "114.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and prayed for the\nfirst time in my life.", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "117.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I told God that I\nwas going to fast,", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "120.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I&#39;d go without food\nand water for 24 hours,", 
            "dur": "4.53", 
            "start": "123.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but that I wanted Him\nto show Himself to me.", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "127.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I fasted.", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "131.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for the first\ntime in eight years,", 
            "dur": "1.85", 
            "start": "134.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I went without\ndrugs and alcohol.", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "135.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But by the next day,\nnothing had happened.", 
            "dur": "4.06", 
            "start": "139.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t want to\nend my life anymore,", 
            "dur": "2.265", 
            "start": "143.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but God never spoke to me.", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "145.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so I forgot about\nthe whole thing.", 
            "dur": "3.675", 
            "start": "148.575"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I knew He didn&#39;t exist.", 
            "dur": "1.055", 
            "start": "152.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I went on with my life.", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "156.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, oddly, a month\nlater an old friend", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "158.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "called, inviting\nme over, a friend", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "162.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I hadn&#39;t seen in five years.", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "165.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we hung out one day,\ncatching up on old times,", 
            "dur": "4.61", 
            "start": "169.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when out of the\nblue he said, &quot;Todd,", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "174.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t know how\nto tell you this.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "176.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was scared to even\ninvite you over.", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "178.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But yesterday I had a\nstrong impression from God", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "181.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to call you.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "183.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And God impressed me to tell you\nthat He needs you on His side,", 
            "dur": "6.81", 
            "start": "185.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "today.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.176", 
            "start": "192.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was speechless.", 
            "dur": "2.989", 
            "start": "195.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Was God real?", 
            "dur": "2.406", 
            "start": "198.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Had He answered my prayer?", 
            "dur": "2.509", 
            "start": "201.311"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Had He sent someone to me?", 
            "dur": "3.242", 
            "start": "203.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I couldn&#39;t believe it.", 
            "dur": "3.058", 
            "start": "207.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But He had.", 
            "dur": "0.565", 
            "start": "210.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With my friend&#39;s help, for\nthe next year and a half,", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "217.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I fought like a lion to\novercome all my problems.", 
            "dur": "3.2", 
            "start": "220.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Up and down I went, succeeding\nand failing along the way.", 
            "dur": "5.49", 
            "start": "223.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But little by little, I started\nto see small but obvious things", 
            "dur": "3.65", 
            "start": "229"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "happen in my life.", 
            "dur": "1.485", 
            "start": "232.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The answers to questions\nthat had long bothered me", 
            "dur": "2.735", 
            "start": "234.135"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "began to be revealed.", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "236.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Slowly things started to change.", 
            "dur": "4.09", 
            "start": "239.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Finally I decided\nto attend church.", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "243.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One day, someone\nthere reached out,", 
            "dur": "2.02", 
            "start": "246.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "inviting me to a\nchurch-sponsored picnic.", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "248.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt a bit awkward about\nit, but I decided to go.", 
            "dur": "5.144", 
            "start": "251.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It turned out to be the\nstraightest party I had ever", 
            "dur": "2.545", 
            "start": "256.664"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "been to: no drugs, no\nalcohol, silly games", 
            "dur": "5.601", 
            "start": "259.209"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the kids\neveryone had brought.", 
            "dur": "2.628", 
            "start": "264.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then we had\nlunch, and someone", 
            "dur": "2.852", 
            "start": "267.438"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wanted to pray\nover the hot dogs.", 
            "dur": "3.322", 
            "start": "270.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought it was strange,\nbut I bowed my head", 
            "dur": "4.288", 
            "start": "273.612"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and closed my eyes.", 
            "dur": "1.405", 
            "start": "277.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then my life changed.", 
            "dur": "3.05", 
            "start": "281.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Two years after that\ninitial fasting prayer,", 
            "dur": "3.59", 
            "start": "284.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "700 days after I had pleaded\nwith God in my closet,", 
            "dur": "4.45", 
            "start": "288.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt something I had never\nfelt in my life, something", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "292.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "20 times stronger than\nany drug I had ever taken.", 
            "dur": "4.29", 
            "start": "296.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was as if someone\nwere hugging me,", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "301"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as if someone were\ntelling me I was home,", 
            "dur": "2.776", 
            "start": "302.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that these people were\ngood, and that I needed", 
            "dur": "4.142", 
            "start": "305.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to be with them,\nthat God was there,", 
            "dur": "3.214", 
            "start": "309.848"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that He knew me by\nname and that He loved me.", 
            "dur": "5.598", 
            "start": "313.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had always thought that if\nGod were to manifest Himself", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "318.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to me that He would come\ndown in a lightning bolt", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "321.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or in a great clash of fire.", 
            "dur": "2.726", 
            "start": "324.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I learned that day at\nthe picnic that I was wrong.", 
            "dur": "3.854", 
            "start": "326.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I realized that it is\npart of our condition", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "330.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as mortals to sometimes\nfeel as though we", 
            "dur": "2.09", 
            "start": "333.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are surrounded by darkness.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "335.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But even though\nwe may feel lost,", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "338.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "God promises to illuminate\nthe way before us, no matter", 
            "dur": "4.031", 
            "start": "341.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how long it takes.", 
            "dur": "3.059", 
            "start": "345.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For two years, God had\nnurtured a questioning soul.", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "348.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Little by little,\nHe had given me", 
            "dur": "1.69", 
            "start": "352.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as much as I could handle until\nthe day I was humble enough", 
            "dur": "3.72", 
            "start": "353.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to hear fully what\nHe wanted to tell me.", 
            "dur": "3.6", 
            "start": "357.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I also learned by\nmy own experience", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "361.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that spiritual\nlight rarely comes", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "363.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to those who merely sit\nin darkness, waiting", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "365.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for someone to flip a switch.", 
            "dur": "2.462", 
            "start": "368.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It takes an act of\nfaith to open our eyes", 
            "dur": "2.673", 
            "start": "370.512"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the light of Christ.", 
            "dur": "2.685", 
            "start": "373.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Twenty years later, I still\ndon&#39;t know everything.", 
            "dur": "3.872", 
            "start": "375.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I now know who I am.", 
            "dur": "3.241", 
            "start": "379.742"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know who God is.", 
            "dur": "3.037", 
            "start": "382.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I know that\nGod&#39;s light is real.", 
            "dur": "4.55", 
            "start": "386.02"
        }
    ], 
